-- EU’s Lewandowski Says Spain Can Ask for Budget Leeway, Efe Says
-- B y   A n g e l i n e   B e n o i t
-- 2012-02-23T10:54:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-23/eu-s-lewandowski-says-spain-can-ask-for-budget-leeway-efe-says.html
The European Commission considers
 Spain ’s plans to overhaul its economy credible enough for the
government to apply for “more tolerance and flexibility”
regarding its budget deficit this year, Efe reported, citing
Janusz Lewandowski, the European Union budget commissioner.  Cinco Dias newspaper carried the Efe story on its website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
